code: @Override protected NamedValueInfo createNamedValueInfo(MethodParameter parameter) {     CookieValue annotation = parameter.getParameterAnnotation(CookieValue.class).     Assert.state(annotation != null, "No CookieValue annotation").     return new CookieValueNamedValueInfo(annotation). }
@Override protected void handleMissingValue(String name, MethodParameter parameter) throws ServletRequestBindingException {     throw new MissingRequestCookieException(name, parameter). }
